14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Gyzamyk
d&uuml;n&yacute;&auml;de gi&#328;den &yacute;a&yacute;ran infeksi&yacute;a
bolmagynda gal&yacute;ar.&nbsp;2018-nji &yacute;ylda Europeewropada 41,000-den
