&yacute;oka&#351;andan b&auml;ri azyndan 37 adamy&#328; &ouml;lendigi habar
berildi.&nbsp;2018-nji &yacute;yly&#328; birinji &yacute;arymynda
&yacute;okan&ccedil; keselleri&#328; sany, 2010-njy &yacute;yldan b&auml;ri
&auml;hli &yacute;yllardaky &yacute;yllyk mukdardan has k&ouml;p.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Immunizasi&yacute;a
programmalary bolmazdan kesel gi&#328;den &yacute;a&yacute;randyr.&nbsp;Gyzamyk
keselini&#328; we &ouml;l&uuml;mi&#328; k&ouml;p&uuml;si saglyk
infrastrukturasy pes girdejili &yacute;urtlarda &yacute;&uuml;ze
&ccedil;yk&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Gyzamyk &ccedil;agalyk keseli
hasaplansa-da, sanjym edilmedik &yacute;a-da b&ouml;lekle&yacute;in sanjym
edilen adamlarda &yacute;a-da immuniteti &yacute;ok adamlarda &yacute;&uuml;ze
&ccedil;ykyp biler.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Alamatlar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Gyzamyk &uuml;&ccedil;in
inkubasi&yacute;a d&ouml;wri 7-14 g&uuml;n (orta&ccedil;a 10-12
g&uuml;n).&nbsp;Ilkinji alamat,&nbsp;adat&ccedil;a 4-7 g&uuml;n dowam
ed&yacute;&auml;n&nbsp;<b>&yacute;okary gyzzyrma&nbsp;</b>(k&ouml;plen&ccedil;&gt;
40 ° C).&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Keseli&#328; katarral
d&ouml;wri&nbsp;</span></b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>n&auml;sazlyk, gyzzyrma, anoreksi&yacute;a we nusgawy
&uuml;&ccedil;l&uuml;k:&nbsp;<b>kon&yacute;uktiwit&nbsp;</b>,&nbsp;<b>&uuml;sg&uuml;lew&uuml;k&nbsp;</b>we&nbsp;<b>burun
akmagy bilen h&auml;si&yacute;etlendiril&yacute;&auml;r&nbsp;</b>.&nbsp;M&uuml;mkin
bolup bil&auml;&yacute;jek be&yacute;leki alamatlar fotofobi&yacute;a,
periorbital &ouml;dem we mialgi&yacute;a.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>D&uuml;w&uuml;rtik
d&ouml;wri&nbsp;</span></b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>keseli&#328; 4-5-nji g&uuml;n&uuml;nden &ouml;s&yacute;&auml;r we
3-4 g&uuml;n dowam ed&yacute;&auml;r, gyzzyrmany&#328;, serho&#351;lygy&#328;,
katarral sindromlary&#328; i&#328; &yacute;okary agyrlygy bilen
h&auml;si&yacute;etlendiril&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Ilkiba&#351;da&nbsp;burnu&#328;
arka tarapynda, gulaklary&#328; a&#328;yrsynda&nbsp;gyzamyk&nbsp;<b>d&ouml;k&uuml;lmesi&nbsp;</b>pe&yacute;da
bol&yacute;ar, ilkinji g&uuml;n &yacute;&uuml;z&uuml;ne, bo&yacute;nuna,
&yacute;okarky d&ouml;&#351;&uuml;ne, egnine &yacute;a&yacute;ra&yacute;ar,
2-nji g&uuml;n bedeni doly &ouml;rt&yacute;&auml;r we &yacute;okarky gollara
&yacute;a&yacute;ra&yacute;ar, 3-4-nji g&uuml;nde &yacute;okarky we a&#351;aky
agzalary doly &ouml;rt&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;D&uuml;w&uuml;rtik
h&auml;si&yacute;eti&#328; d&ouml;remegi, do&yacute;gun g&uuml;lg&uuml;ne
re&#328;k, ilki ki&ccedil;i, birn&auml;&ccedil;e sagatdan so&#328; elementler
k&ouml;pel&yacute;&auml;r, birle&#351;&yacute;&auml;r, uly, tertipsiz
&#351;ekilli a&ccedil;yk gyzyl elementleri emele
getir&yacute;&auml;r;&nbsp;agzalary&#328; da&#351;ky we i&ccedil;ki
&yacute;&uuml;zlerinde derini&#328; &uuml;&yacute;tgeme&yacute;&auml;n fonunda
&yacute;erle&#351;&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;D&uuml;w&uuml;rtik pe&yacute;da
bolanda, temperaturany&#328; t&auml;ze &yacute;okarlanmagy
h&auml;si&yacute;etlidir (&nbsp;<b>iki tolkunly gyzzyrma&nbsp;</b>).&nbsp;D&uuml;w&uuml;rtik
d&ouml;k&uuml;lmesi bilen bir wagty&#328; &ouml;z&uuml;nde gyzamyk
keselini&#328; h&auml;si&yacute;etli alamaty go&#351;ul&yacute;ar -&nbsp;<b>Belski&yacute;
- Filatow - Koplik tegmilleri&nbsp;</b>- adat&ccedil;a
&yacute;a&#328;aklary&#328; gyjyndyrmalarynda ownuk mollara gar&#351;y,
k&ouml;plen&ccedil; dodaklary&#328; we di&#351; etlerini&#328;
gyjyndyrmalarynda bol&yacute;ar.&nbsp;D&uuml;w&uuml;rtikler ownuk,
&ccedil;al-ak bolup, gyzyllygy&#328; dar ara&ccedil;&auml;gi bilen
gur&#351;alan, biri-biri bilen birle&#351;m&auml;n, 2-3 g&uuml;n dowam
ed&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Bar&#351;ynda&nbsp;<b>pigmentasyonun
d&ouml;wr&uuml;nde&nbsp;</b>howlukma&ccedil;lyk &ccedil;alt
k&uuml;teld&yacute;&auml;ndir we go&#328;ur tonuyla
galdyr&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Pigmentasi&yacute;a d&ouml;k&uuml;lme
d&ouml;wr&uuml;ni&#328; 3-nji g&uuml;n&uuml;nden &yacute;&uuml;ze
&ccedil;yk&yacute;ar we d&ouml;k&uuml;lm&auml;ni&#328; da&#351;ky
g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;i &yacute;aly tertipde, k&auml;te gabyk bilen gutar&yacute;ar.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Gyzamyky&#328; atipiki
wariantlaryna gow&#351;adylan, abort, &yacute;ok edilen, asimptomatiki
g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;ler gir&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Keseli&#328; diagnozy</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Sorag we g&ouml;zleg</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>N&auml;sagy&#328; keseli&#328;
d&ouml;remegini&#328; tebigaty, gyzzyrma, dowamlylygy, n&auml;sazlygy&#328;
&yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;ykmagy, kelle agyry, ukyny&#328; bozulmagy, &yacute;&uuml;rek
bulanma, gusmak, bokurdak agyry, g&ouml;z agyry, fotofobi&yacute;a,
&uuml;sg&uuml;lew&uuml;k, burun akmagy barada d&uuml;&yacute;pli g&ouml;zleg
ge&ccedil;iril&yacute;&auml;r. we adaty
d&ouml;k&uuml;lmeler.&nbsp;S&ouml;hbetde&#351;likde gyzamyk we / &yacute;a-da
d&ouml;k&uuml;lme bilen &yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;yk&yacute;an islendik
n&auml;sag bilen aragatna&#351;yga &uuml;ns beril&yacute;&auml;r,
&yacute;oka&#351;magy&#328; &yacute;ollary
a&yacute;dy&#328;la&#351;dyryl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Gyzamyka we / &yacute;a-da
immunoglobulini kabul etmeklige yzygiderli we gyssagly sanjym maglumatlary
beril&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Lukman hassany g&ouml;zden
ge&ccedil;irende, bedeni&#328; gyzgynlygyny &ouml;l&ccedil;&auml;r, derini,
agyz mukozasyny, g&ouml;zleri barla&yacute;ar, d&ouml;k&uuml;lm&auml;ni&#328;
tebigatyna we katarral sindromy&#328; agyrlygyna baha ber&yacute;&auml;r,
&ouml;&yacute;keni&#328; auskultasi&yacute;asyny (di&#328;lemegini)
&yacute;erine &yacute;etir&yacute;&auml;r, a&#328;y&#328; peselmegini&#328;
derejesini kesgitle&yacute;&auml;r we newrologiki alamatlar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Laboratori&yacute;a barlagy</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Serologiki anykla&yacute;y&#351; usuly&nbsp;(ELISA)&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>.&nbsp;Gandaky
&yacute;adro a&yacute;ratyn IgM antikorlaryny&#328; tapylmagy &yacute;iti
&yacute;okan&ccedil;lygy g&ouml;rkez&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Du&yacute;gurlyk
d&ouml;r&auml;p ba&#351;landan 3-14 g&uuml;n so&#328; i&#328;
&yacute;okarydyr.&nbsp;IgG antikorlaryny&#328; bolmagy &ouml;&#328;ki infeksi&yacute;any
&yacute;a-da &ouml;&#328;&uuml;nden sanjymy
g&ouml;rkez&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;IgG antikorlaryny&#328; titrini&#328;
j&uuml;b&uuml;t gan serasyny bir wagtda &ouml;wrenmek bilen 4 &yacute;a-da
ondanam k&ouml;p &yacute;okarlanmagy diagnoz &uuml;&ccedil;in esas bolup
dur&yacute;ar.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Molekul&yacute;ar biologiki anykla&yacute;y&#351; usuly
(PCR)&nbsp;</span></b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>.&nbsp;Gyzamyk RNK-ny bokurdakdan, burundan, nazofarinksden
&yacute;a-da pe&#351;ewden &ccedil;i&#351;irip bol&yacute;ar.&nbsp;&#350;ol bir
hassany&#328; birn&auml;&ccedil;e nusgasyny barlamak, wirusy&#328;
izol&yacute;asi&yacute;a &auml;htimallygyny ep-esli
&yacute;okarlandyr&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Mundan ba&#351;ga-da, d&ouml;k&uuml;n
d&ouml;remeginden 1-3 g&uuml;n so&#328; nusgalar &yacute;ygnalanda wirusy&#328;
d&ouml;k&uuml;lmegi &auml;htimallygy has uludyr, &yacute;&ouml;ne wirus
d&ouml;k&uuml;lm&auml;ni&#328; ba&#351;lanmagyndan 10-14 g&uuml;n so&#328;
&yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;ykyp biler.</span></p>

