color:black'>Kabul edilen maslahatlara la&yacute;yklykda janly wirus gyzamyk sanjymy
bilen sanjym profilaktikasy.&nbsp;</span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Ilaty&#328; immunitetini&#328;
&yacute;okary derejesini saklamak we gyzamyk keselini &yacute;ok etmek
&uuml;&ccedil;in BSGG, ilaty&#328; 95% -inden gowragyny iki doza gyzamyk
sanjymy bilen sanjym etmegi maslahat ber&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>6 a&yacute;dan 1 &yacute;a&#351;a &ccedil;enli &auml;hli halkara
sy&yacute;ahat&ccedil;ylar, barmaly &yacute;erine garamazdan, gyzamyk
sanjymyny&#328; bir dozasyny, 1 &yacute;a&#351;a we ondan uly &yacute;a&#351;ly
halkara sy&yacute;ahat&ccedil;ylara iki dozada gyzamyk sanjymyny almaly
(i&#328; az aralyk sanjymlar - 28 g&uuml;n).</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Sickarawsyz adamlary du&yacute;gur adamlardan izolirlemek,
potensial aragatna&#351;yklary immunla&#351;dyrmak we &yacute;&uuml;ze
